title: Mens Deep Green Blazer
short_des: Add a touch of casual elegance with this men's blazer. Made from a cotton blend, this unlined, unpadded blazer features relaxed lapels for a less formal, more comfortable fit. The slim fit design is lightweight, making it perfect for layering over various outfits for both style and ease.
remark: Wash dark colors separately. Do not bleach. Wash mild detergent
